{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# AI Metadata Enricher -- Pipeline Dashboard\n\nThe AI Metadata Enricher automatically processes enterprise data assets, generating AI-driven metadata descriptions with built-in quality controls and idempotency safeguards.\n\nThis dashboard provides real-time operational visibility into every execution, showing what the system decided, why, and how long it took. All data is sourced from `pipeline_completion` trace events in Application Insights.\n\n---"
      },
      "name": "header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "time-range",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                { "durationMs": 3600000, "text": "Last 1 hour" },
                { "durationMs": 14400000, "text": "Last 4 hours" },
                { "durationMs": 86400000, "text": "Last 24 hours" },
                { "durationMs": 259200000, "text": "Last 3 days" },
                { "durationMs": 604800000, "text": "Last 7 days" }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            },
            "label": "Time Range"
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Section 1: System Overview",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## System Overview\n\nThese KPIs summarize the total volume of executions, the proportion that resulted in successful enrichment, and the average end-to-end processing time. A healthy system shows a stable success rate and consistent latency.\n\n> **About human review:** When an asset has a description awaiting human approval (lifecycle = PENDING), the system continues monitoring it for changes but does not overwrite the description automatically. If the asset changes during the review period, the execution is recorded as **Pending Review — Content Changed** — this is not an error. It is the system signaling that the asset under review has been modified and the reviewer should be aware."
            },
            "name": "section1-text"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let data = traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| summarize\n    TotalExecutions = count(),\n    Successes = countif(tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]) == \"SUCCESS\"),\n    AvgLatencyMs = coalesce(round(avg(toint(customDimensions[\"durationMs\"])), 0), 0.0)\n| extend SuccessRatePct = iff(TotalExecutions > 0, round(100.0 * Successes / TotalExecutions, 1), 0.0);\nprint x=1 | project Metric = 'Total Executions', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project TotalExecutions))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'Success Rate (%)', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project SuccessRatePct)))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'Avg Latency (ms)', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project AvgLatencyMs)))",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Pipeline KPIs",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 0,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 1
                    }
                  }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "name": "overview-kpi-tiles"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| extend rawStatus = tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"])\n| extend DisplayStatus = case(\n    rawStatus == \"SUCCESS\", \"Successfully Enriched\",\n    rawStatus == \"SKIP\", \"Already Processed\",\n    rawStatus == \"NO_CONTEXT\", \"Insufficient Context\",\n    rawStatus == \"BLOCK\", \"Validation Protected\",\n    rawStatus == \"ERROR\", \"Processing Error\",\n    rawStatus == \"PENDING_PROTECTED\", \"Pending Review — Content Changed\",\n    \"Unknown\"\n  )\n| summarize Count = count() by DisplayStatus\n| order by Count desc",
              "size": 2,
              "title": "Execution Outcome Distribution",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  { "seriesName": "Successfully Enriched", "color": "green" },
                  { "seriesName": "Already Processed", "color": "blue" },
                  { "seriesName": "Insufficient Context", "color": "orange" },
                  { "seriesName": "Validation Protected", "color": "redBright" },
                  { "seriesName": "Processing Error", "color": "red" },
                  { "seriesName": "Pending Review — Content Changed", "color": "yellow" }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "overview-status-pie"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| extend rawStatus = tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"])\n| extend DisplayStatus = case(\n    rawStatus == \"SUCCESS\", \"Successfully Enriched\",\n    rawStatus == \"SKIP\", \"Already Processed\",\n    rawStatus == \"NO_CONTEXT\", \"Insufficient Context\",\n    rawStatus == \"BLOCK\", \"Validation Protected\",\n    rawStatus == \"ERROR\", \"Processing Error\",\n    rawStatus == \"PENDING_PROTECTED\", \"Pending Review — Content Changed\",\n    \"Unknown\"\n  )\n| summarize Count = count() by\n    bin(timestamp, 1h),\n    DisplayStatus\n| order by timestamp asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Execution Trend Over Time",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "timechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  { "seriesName": "Successfully Enriched", "color": "green" },
                  { "seriesName": "Already Processed", "color": "blue" },
                  { "seriesName": "Insufficient Context", "color": "orange" },
                  { "seriesName": "Validation Protected", "color": "redBright" },
                  { "seriesName": "Processing Error", "color": "red" },
                  { "seriesName": "Pending Review — Content Changed", "color": "yellow" }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "overview-status-trend"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "group-overview"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Section 2: Decision Breakdown",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Decision Breakdown\n\nEvery execution results in one of five outcomes, each reflecting a deliberate decision by the system's quality and safety controls.\n\n| Outcome | Meaning |\n|---|---|\n| **Successfully Enriched** | Asset received a new AI-generated metadata description |\n| **Already Processed** | Asset was unchanged since last run -- no re-enrichment needed (hash match) |\n| **Insufficient Context** | No grounding data available in the knowledge base -- enrichment safely aborted to prevent ungrounded output |\n| **Validation Protected** | AI output did not meet quality standards -- write-back to the catalog was blocked |\n| **Pending Review — Content Changed** | Asset has a description awaiting human approval AND its content changed since the description was written. The system detected the change but did not overwrite the description under review. This is expected governance behavior, not an error. |\n| **Processing Error** | A transient or unexpected error occurred -- the message will be retried automatically |"
            },
            "name": "section2-text"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| extend rawStatus = tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"])\n| extend DisplayStatus = case(\n    rawStatus == \"SUCCESS\", \"Successfully Enriched\",\n    rawStatus == \"SKIP\", \"Already Processed\",\n    rawStatus == \"NO_CONTEXT\", \"Insufficient Context\",\n    rawStatus == \"BLOCK\", \"Validation Protected\",\n    rawStatus == \"ERROR\", \"Processing Error\",\n    rawStatus == \"PENDING_PROTECTED\", \"Pending Review — Content Changed\",\n    \"Unknown\"\n  )\n| summarize Count = count() by DisplayStatus\n| extend Total = toscalar(\n    traces\n    | where timestamp {TimeRange}\n    | where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n    | count\n  )\n| extend Percentage = round(100.0 * Count / Total, 1)\n| project DisplayStatus, Count, Percentage\n| order by Count desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Decision Distribution",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Percentage",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    },
                    "numberFormat": {
                      "unit": 1,
                      "options": {
                        "style": "decimal",
                        "maximumFractionDigits": 1
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DisplayStatus",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Successfully Enriched", "representation": "green", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Already Processed", "representation": "blue", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Insufficient Context", "representation": "orange", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Validation Protected", "representation": "redBright", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Processing Error", "representation": "red", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Pending Review — Content Changed", "representation": "yellow", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "Default", "representation": "lightBlue", "text": "{0}{1}" }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "decision-table"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "group-decisions"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Section 3: Pipeline Performance",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Pipeline Performance\n\nThe pipeline processes assets end-to-end, with the LLM invocation as the primary latency factor. Assets that exit early (Already Processed, Insufficient Context) complete in under 200ms. Full enrichment cycles including LLM invocation and catalog writeback typically complete in under 6 seconds."
            },
            "name": "section3-text"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| where isnotempty(customDimensions[\"durationMs\"])\n| extend DurationMs = toint(customDimensions[\"durationMs\"])\n| summarize\n    AvgMs = round(avg(DurationMs), 0),\n    P50Ms = round(percentile(DurationMs, 50), 0),\n    P95Ms = round(percentile(DurationMs, 95), 0),\n    MaxMs = max(DurationMs),\n    Executions = count()\n  by Stage = tostring(customDimensions[\"stage\"])\n| where isnotempty(Stage)\n| order by AvgMs desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Latency by Pipeline Stage",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AvgMs",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "yellowOrangeRed"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "P95Ms",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "yellowOrangeRed"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "latency-table"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let data = traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| where toint(customDimensions[\"tokenCount\"]) > 0\n| summarize\n    TotalTokens = sum(toint(customDimensions[\"tokenCount\"])),\n    AvgTokens = round(avg(toint(customDimensions[\"tokenCount\"])), 0),\n    LLMInvocations = count()\n| extend EstimatedCostUSD = round(toreal(TotalTokens) * 0.000005, 4);\nprint x=1 | project Metric = 'Total Tokens', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project TotalTokens))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'Avg Tokens/Call', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project AvgTokens)))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'LLM Invocations', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project LLMInvocations)))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'Est. Cost (USD)', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project EstimatedCostUSD)))",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "LLM Token Usage",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 0,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 4
                    }
                  }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "token-usage"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "group-performance"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Section 4: Reliability",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Reliability\n\nThe system is designed to fail safely -- errors result in message retry via Service Bus dead-letter, never silent data corruption. A Validation Protected outcome means the AI output was caught by quality controls before reaching the catalog. Both scenarios demonstrate the system working as intended.\n\nAn increasing error rate or sustained block rate may indicate a configuration issue, a change in source data quality, or an LLM behavior regression that warrants investigation."
            },
            "name": "section4-text"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let data = traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| summarize\n    Total = count(),\n    Errors = countif(tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]) == \"ERROR\"),\n    Blocked = countif(tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]) == \"BLOCK\")\n| extend ErrorRatePct = iff(Total > 0, round(100.0 * Errors / Total, 1), 0.0)\n| extend BlockRatePct = iff(Total > 0, round(100.0 * Blocked / Total, 1), 0.0);\nprint x=1 | project Metric = 'Error Rate (%)', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project ErrorRatePct))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'Block Rate (%)', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project BlockRatePct)))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'Total Errors', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project Errors)))\n| union (print x=1 | project Metric = 'Total Blocked', Value = toreal(toscalar(data | project Blocked)))",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Error & Block Rates",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Metric",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
                    "unit": 0,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "maximumFractionDigits": 1
                    }
                  }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "name": "reliability-kpi-tiles"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| summarize\n    Total = count(),\n    Errors = countif(tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]) == \"ERROR\")\n  by bin(timestamp, 1h)\n| extend ErrorRatePct = iff(Total > 0, round(100.0 * Errors / Total, 1), 0.0)\n| project timestamp, ErrorRatePct",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Error Rate Trend (hourly)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "timechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "ySettings": {
                  "min": 0
                }
              }
            },
            "name": "error-rate-trend"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "traces\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where customDimensions[\"event\"] == \"pipeline_completion\"\n| where tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]) == \"BLOCK\" or tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]) == \"ERROR\"\n| project\n    Timestamp = timestamp,\n    CorrelationId = tostring(customDimensions[\"correlationId\"]),\n    Status = tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]),\n    Stage = tostring(customDimensions[\"stage\"]),\n    ValidationStatus = tostring(customDimensions[\"validationStatus\"]),\n    DurationMs = toint(customDimensions[\"durationMs\"])\n| order by Timestamp desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Recent Blocked & Error Executions",
              "noDataMessage": "No blocked or error executions in the selected time range -- the system is operating cleanly.",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Status",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "BLOCK", "representation": "redBright", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "ERROR", "representation": "red", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "Default", "representation": "lightBlue", "text": "{0}{1}" }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "failures-detail-table"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "group-reliability"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Section 5: Execution Trace Explorer",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Execution Trace Explorer\n\nEnter any correlationId to see the complete audit trail of a single execution. Every pipeline run carries a unique correlationId that links all events from message receipt through to the final catalog write-back (or early exit). This provides full traceability for compliance, debugging, and operational review."
            },
            "name": "section5-text"
          },
          {
            "type": 9,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
              "parameters": [
                {
                  "id": "correlation-id",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "CorrelationId",
                  "type": 1,
                  "isRequired": false,
                  "value": "",
                  "label": "Correlation ID"
                }
              ],
              "style": "pills",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components"
            },
            "name": "trace-parameters"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "traces\n| where timestamp > ago(7d)\n| where strlen(\"{CorrelationId}\") > 0\n| where tostring(customDimensions[\"correlationId\"]) == \"{CorrelationId}\"\n| project\n    Timestamp = timestamp,\n    Event = message,\n    Stage = tostring(customDimensions[\"stage\"]),\n    Status = tostring(customDimensions[\"status\"]),\n    DurationMs = toint(customDimensions[\"durationMs\"]),\n    Element = tostring(customDimensions[\"elementName\"]),\n    EventType = tostring(customDimensions[\"event\"])\n| order by Timestamp asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Trace for Correlation ID",
              "noDataMessage": "Enter a Correlation ID above to view the execution trace. You can copy one from the Recent Executions table below.",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Status",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "colors",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "SUCCESS", "representation": "green", "text": "{0}{1}" },
